node.text: I stand with the Palestinian people and support their resistance to colonization and protection of their human rights. My heart aches for the families who have lost loved ones. We can not stand as silent witnesses to children being orphaned and murdered and not demand for the human rights of all Palestinians!  This must end. Free Palestine.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'COM PLEX NEWS WHAT'S HAPPENING IN SHEIK JARRAH'.

Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of monument and text that says 'ON MAY7 & 10, ISRAELI FORCES STORMED AL AQSA MOSQUE IN JERUSALEM AND UNLEASHED TEAR GAS, STUN GRENADES, AND RUBBER TIPPED BULLETS ON PALESTINIAN WORSHIPPERS.'.

Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and text that says 'THE VIOLENCE TOOK PLACE DURING THE FINAL DAYS OF RAMADAN, WHICH IS THE HOLIEST MONTH FOR MUSLIMS. AL AQSA MOSQUE IS THE THIRD HOLIEST SITE FOR MUSLIMS.'.

Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'PALESTINIANS REMAINED AT AL AQSA MOSQUE AFTER EVENING PRAYERS IN ORDER TO PROTEST ISRAEL'S PLANS TO FORCIBLY EVICT MORETHAN 200 PALESTINIANS FROM THEIR HOMES IN THE SHEIK JARRAH NEIGHBORHOOD OF EAST JERUSALEM. THE LATEST EVICTIONS COME FROM A 73-YEAR-OI YEAR- MILITARY OCCUPATION AGAINST PALESTINIANS, WHICH BEGAN IN 1948.'.

Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MORE THAN 300 PALESTINIANS WERE HOSPITALIZED THIS WEEK, WITH AT LEAST 25 ANNOUNCED DEAD, INCLUDING 10 CHILDREN, AFTER ISRAELI AIR STRIKES HIT GAZA. HAMAS LATER LAUNCHED ROCKETS INTO ISRAEL IN RETALIATION, REPORTEDLY KILLING 3 ISRAELIS, AND INJURING OVER 100. PN'.

Photo by Zayn Malik on May 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'THE VIOLENCE THAT HAS ERUPTED ACROSS JERUSALEM IS A CULMINATION OF RISING TENSION AND PROTEST IN THE OCCUPIED PALESTINIAN TERRITORIES.'.

Photo shared by Zayn Malik on April 03, 2021 tagging @gqindia, and @petros_koy. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'INDIA Ge SUMMER 2021 Where To Travel Now แลา EVERYBODY IS LISTENING TO ZAYN MALIK'.

Photo shared by Zayn Malik on April 03, 2021 tagging @gqindia, and @petros_koy. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'INDIA Ge SUMMER 2021 Where To Travel Now แลา EVERYBODY IS LISTENING TO ZAYN MALIK'.

Photo shared by Zayn Malik on April 03, 2021 tagging @gqspain, and @petros_koy. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'ZAYN MIGUEL ÁNGEL SILVESTRE FRIEDRICH KUNATH OLLYALEXANDER DOMENICO DOLCE STEFANOGABA STEFANO GABBANA JOHN WATERS ALBARECHE ELS NO LABELS NO NOU'.
